Catalogues are collections of endpoints that are relevant to the data segmentation on some of the other endpoints.

#### List of Catalogues: 

1. Date Formats
2. Webhook Event Types



#### Date Formats

```json
{
    "id_date_format": "5e961923bebbce48bd7601aa",
    // The ID of the date format
    "name": "Unix Timestamp"
    // String; The name of the Date Format
}
```

#### Webhook Event Types

```json
{
    "id_attachment_type": "5ed54ea7f79417520c0015b9",
    // SyncID; The ID of the Attachment Type assignated by Paybook Sync
    "name": "payments.transaction_created"
    // String; The name of the Account Type
}
```

